lines.text: I hoped you let me stay around for a while.
I don't think you'd like ranching. It's hard work.
Do I! I parlayed a two dollar bet into a bundle that big!
[Sue holds her fingers three inches apart]
[Sue and Jefferson are conversing on the phone]
Suzy, pet, you've done it! Who is he, where did you find him and where are you?
In Whispering Rock. A town? Heh-heh. It's a mudpie with people.
Maybe you can parlay that into a lot.
Oh, can I! Will you help me bring in my bags?
Not in here! We have a nice cozy little room - in the barn.
The barn! Oh. Well, how delightfully rustic.
